### Crear pagador (el tercero debe existir previamente)
POST {{base}}/api/payers
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thirdPartyId": 8,
  "code": "EPS-SURA-01",
  "payerTypeId": 23,
  "clientTypeId": 9,
  "epsCode": "EPS010",
  "administratorCode": null,
  "filingDays": 30,
  "glossaResponseDays": 15
}

###

### Obtener por ID
GET {{base}}/api/payers/3
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener por tercero
GET {{base}}/api/payers/third/8
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Listar con paginación
POST {{base}}/api/payers/list
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 0,
  "rows": 10,
  "search": "",
  "order_by": "t.nombre_completo",
  "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar
PUT {{base}}/api/payers/1
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payerTypeId": 1,
  "clientTypeId": 1,
  "epsCode": "EPS010",
  "administratorCode": "ADM001",
  "filingDays": 45,
  "glossaResponseDays": 20
}

###

### Activar/Inactivar
PATCH {{base}}/api/payers/1/toggle-active
Authorization: {{token}}
